instructText: The next part of the experiment is to recall each story to the best of your ability.
You will be presented with the story title, names, the images, and a blank text box for each story.
Write as much as you can remember about each story. Try to include everything, even if it seems trivial.
When you are finished recalling one story, to move onto the next one hit ‘tab’.
There is no time limit for your responses.
